Real-Time Emotion-Based Music Player:

Overview:

The Real-Time Emotion-Based Music Player is an AI-powered application that detects a user's facial emotion through a webcam and automatically recommends or plays music based on the detected emotion. The system combines Computer Vision and Machine Learning to create a personalized and interactive music experience.

Features:

Real-time face detection using webcam
Facial emotion recognition
Automatic music recommendation based on emotion
Supports multiple emotions such as Happy, Sad, Angry, Neutral, and Surprise
User-friendly interface
Fast and accurate emotion detection


Tech Stack:

Programming Language: Python
Computer Vision: OpenCV
Machine Learning / Deep Learning: TensorFlow, Keras
Emotion Detection: FER (Facial Emotion Recognition)
Data Processing: NumPy
Music Playback: Pygame
GUI (Optional): Tkinter

