Installation:

1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Paulrex1404/Real-Time-Emotion-Based-Music-Player.git
2. Navigate to the project folder
cd Real-Time-Emotion-Based-Music-Player
3. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
4. Run the application
python app.py

How It Works:

The webcam captures the user's face.
OpenCV detects the face in real time.
The trained emotion recognition model predicts the user's emotion.
The predicted emotion is mapped to a music playlist.
The corresponding song is automatically played.
